Zöe Lucker https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Z%C3%B6e_Lucker 0 Zöe Elizabeth Lucker (born 11 April 1974 in Huddersfield, West Yorkshire) is an English actress. Her roles on television include Tanya Turner on ITV's Footballers' Wives, with a crossover appearance in Bad Girls, Vanessa Gold in EastEnders, Carol Barry in Waterloo Road and Reenie McQueen in Hollyoaks.
